You wake up in a maze. Is it a problem to find an escape? Usualy it is not. But you feel your memory is leaking. And several dangerous guys are getting closely. It's time to run through the maze and beat some enemies. At one moment you will find a vendor or several of them. But don't trust them. They will take your life and your memory as a part of your life.

![minimap.gif](///raw/82f/21/z/23979.gif)

Control:
wasd - move;
h - heal;
space - melee attack;
e - range attack.

